          <span class="sr-only">View Cart</span>
          <svg class="h-6 w-6 text-current" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink" version="1.1" width="256" height="256" viewBox="0 0 256 256" xml:space="preserve">
